  "abstract": "Not much information is available about the usefulness of foxtail millet germplasm in\r\nbreeding programmes. A composite collection of 500 accessions has been developed and\r\nmolecularly profiled using 19 SSRs (Xia et al. 2007; Dida et al. 2007; ICRISAT\r\nunpublished data) in high throughput assay (ABI3700).",
